      <title>对美联储转向的押注推动标准普尔 500 指数创下两年来的首次纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/bets-on-a-fed-pivot-drive-s-p-500-to-first-record-in-two-years</link>
