      <title>据称，3R 持有人敦促银行并购巴西石油公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/3r-petroleum-is-said-to-tap-banks-as-holder-urges-brazil-oil-m-a</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，巴西石油初级企业 3R Petroleum Oleo e Gas SA 已聘请银行就一项潜在交易提供咨询，此前该公司的一名股东提交了与当地钻探公司 PetroReconcavo SA 进行公司重组的提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/3r-petroleum-is-said-to-tap-banks-as-holder-urges-brazil-oil-m-a</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 16:59:46 GMT</pubDate>
